ABSOLUTELY CERTAIN

36:44.000 --> 36:45.667
THAT THERE'S NO WAY
TO BRIDGE THE GAP?

36:47.917 --> 36:49.083
[SIGHS]

36:49.083 --> 36:50.708
I WAS HOPING
THAT THERE WOULD BE,

36:50.708 --> 36:52.458
BUT I...

36:52.458 --> 36:55.542
DON'T THINK THAT'S
GONNA HAPPEN.

36:55.542 --> 36:57.917
DAWSON...

37:00.208 --> 37:02.500
