A PROBLEM,

37:21.750 --> 37:22.708
IT GETS BIGGER.

37:22.708 --> 37:24.792
AND IF THERE'S
CLOSENESS...

37:24.792 --> 37:27.041
YOU GET CLOSER.

37:29.041 --> 37:31.041
AS FAR AS YOU
AND GRETCHEN
ARE CONCERNED,

37:31.041 --> 37:31.917
I MEAN...

37:31.917 --> 37:34.083
YOU GUYS ARE
PROBABLY A LOT CLOSER

37:34.083 --> 37:36.959
THAN A LOT OF PEOPLE
