A LOT OF COAXING.

38:25.291 --> 38:27.625
HOW DID YOU FINALLY GET
HER TO CHANGE HER MIND?

38:27.625 --> 38:31.041
OH, I JUST STARTED
CALLING OUT HER NAME.

38:31.041 --> 38:33.917
"LILLIAN, LILLIAN.

38:33.917 --> 38:36.208
EVERYONE'S WAITING
TO MEET YOU."

38:36.917 --> 38:40.291
AND THERE SHE WAS.

38:41.583 --> 38:43.250
LILLIAN.

38:44.291 --> 38:45.917
HONEY, DO YOU
WANT TO HOLD HER?

38:45.917 --> 38:47.959
[LILLIAN COUGHS]

38:47.959 --> 38:50.417
OH, YEAH.

38:51.917 --> 38:53.333
[WHISPERING]
There we go.

38:54.625 --> 38:56.834
There we go.

39:01.333 --> 39:03.333
HELLO, LILLIAN.

39:04.000 --> 39:07.291
I'M DAWSON...

39:07.291 --> 39:08.500
YOUR BIG BROTHER.

39:13.542 --> 39:15.583
[LAUGHS]

39:15.583 --> 39:17.250
[LAUGHS]

39:17.250 --> 39:19.542
WELCOME
TO OUR FAMILY.

39:19.542 --> 39:22.000
YOU COULDN'T HAVE
PICKED A BETTER ONE.

39:50.917 --> 39:52.792
[RING]

39:53.291 --> 39:54.208
HELLO.

39:54.208 --> 39:55.291
HEY, GRETCHEN
TOLD ME

39:55.291 --> 39:57.375
I HAD TO CALL
IMMEDIATELY.
WHAT'S WRONG?

39:58.542 --> 39:59.500
ACTUALLY, NOTHING.

39:59.500 --> 40:03.208
I THOUGHT I HAD
A HUGE PROBLEM,

40:03.208 --> 40:04.834
BUT, UM...

40:04.834 --> 40:06.041
I WAS WRONG.

40:06.041 --> 40:07.500
WELL, WHAT KIND
OF PROBLEM DID YOU
THINK YOU HAD?

40:07.500 --> 40:11.125
IT'S NOTHING THAT
YOU SHOULD WORRY ABOUT.

40:13.375 --> 40:16.708
THE IMPORTANT THING IS
THAT YOU FOCUS ON YOURSELF.

40:19.583 --> 40:21.959
WHERE ARE YOU?

40:24.875 --> 40:25.542
I TOLD YOU, I'M
FISHING WITH DOUGIE.

40:27.750 --> 40:29.417
WE'RE HAVING THE TIME
OF OUR LIVES OUT HERE.

40:29.417 --> 40:32.417
CAUGHT A 90-POUND
MARLIN YESTERDAY.

40:32.417 --> 40:34.125
WE'RE LIVING
THE HIGH LIFE, JO.

40:34.125 --> 40:37.583
THE HIGH LIFE.

40:37.583 --> 40:39.917
YOU AND I GOT TO GET
OUT HERE SOME TIME.

40:45.041 --> 40:48.583
YEAH, WE WILL.

40:48.583 --> 40:50.542
WE'LL HAVE TO DO
THAT REAL SOON.

40:53.250 --> 40:54.417
YEAH.

40:55.333 --> 40:55.542
I MISS YOU.

40:58.917 --> 41:00.750
I MISS YOU, PACE.

41:36.750 --> 41:38.458
I THOUGHT YOU HAD
A TRAIN TO CATCH.

41:40.125 --> 41:41.750
YOU KNOW THE BEST
THING ABOUT TRAINS?

41:43.166 --> 41:45.000
THERE'S ALWAYS
A LATER ONE.

41:59.041 --> 42:00.583
[LAUGHS]

42:00.583 --> 42:02.250
THIS IS CRAZY.

42:02.250 --> 42:03.458
INSANE.

42:04.458 --> 42:06.083
WHAT ARE WE DOING?

42:06.083 --> 42:07.208
PROLONGING
THE INEVITABLE.

42:07.208 --> 42:10.625
LIVING IN DENIAL.

42:10.625 --> 42:12.792
WHO KNEW DENIAL COULD
FEEL THIS GOOD?

42:13.875 --> 42:15.667
YOU KNOW THERE'S
NO HOPE FOR US.

42:15.667 --> 42:16.834
HOW COULD THERE BE?

42:16.834 --> 42:18.208
WE'RE HEADED IN COMPLETELY
DIFFERENT DIRECTIONS.

42:18.208 --> 42:19.583
WE MIGHT AS WELL BE GOING
TO 2 DIFFERENT PLANETS.

42:19.583 --> 42:22.792
WE SHOULD REALLY
BREAK UP RIGHT NOW.

42:22.792 --> 42:24.041
JUST GET IT OVER WITH.

42:24.041 --> 42:24.875
I AGREE.

42:24.875 --> 42:27.875
I NEVER WANT
TO SEE YOU AGAIN.
